title: Watch how a University professor tries to link the Catalan independence movement to violence
description:
Understanding Catalonia @UnderstandingCa

Watch how a University professor tries to link the Catalan independence movement to violence and ends up changing the subject when he is asked to give a single example of such violence. A presenter of Al Jazeera, one of the most watched TVs worldwide, loses his patience after dealing with the manners of Enric Martínez, a unionist professor and supporter of Tabarnia.
